snippet.title: Army Attack Gameplay
snippet.description:
Army Attack is a game where you are the general of an army to take down enemies and complete missions! Check it out: http://adf.ly/OQFJJ

♨Check out our website: http://adf.ly/OOwCG Hello guys! I recently got into app development and decided to make this simple unit converter for my first android (no ios yet) project as a newbie. If you're interested and would like to check it out, just click the link below to go to the play store. Thank you so much if you do!
